{
  "title": "SC-002A 废弃仓库 - 相信神秘人路线",
  "scenes": [
    {
      "frame": "https://lost-choices-art.tos-cn-beijing.volces.com/scenes/ch1/sc_002/sc_002_env_01_20260222_091751_1.png",
      "text": "那个人说这里有人接应我...这里就是废弃仓库...好安静...",
      "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural"
    },
    {
      "frame": "https://lost-choices-art.tos-cn-beijing.volces.com/scenes/ch1/sc_002/sc_002_env_01_20260222_091751_1.png",
      "text": "月光从破损的窗户射入...这里废弃很久了...",
      "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural"
    },
    {
      "frame": "https://lost-choices-art.tos-cn-beijing.volces.com/characters/lin_xiaowei/lin_xiaowei_pose_01_20260222_043941_1.png",
      "text": "你终于来了。我还以为你不会出现。",
      "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural"
    },
    {
      "frame": "https://lost-choices-art.tos-cn-beijing.volces.com/characters/lin_xiaowei/lin_xiaowei_pose_01_20260222_043941_1.png",
      "text": "别紧张。我是林晓薇。那个人让我来接你。",
      "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural"
    },
    {
      "frame": "https://lost-choices-art.tos-cn-beijing.volces.com/characters/lin_xiaowei/lin_xiaowei_face_03_20260222_042138_1.png",
      "text": "我知道你现在有很多疑问，但我们时间不多。追兵可能已经在路上了。",
      "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural"
    },
    {
      "frame": "https://lost-choices-art.tos-cn-beijing.volces.com/scenes/ch1/sc_002/sc_002_env_01_20260222_091751_1.png",
      "text": "她知道我失忆了？她和那个神秘人是什么关系？我能相信她吗？",
      "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural"
    },
    {
      "frame": "https://lost-choices-art.tos-cn-beijing.volces.com/characters/lin_xiaowei/lin_xiaowei_face_04_20260222_042754_1.png",
      "text": "听着，我不知道那个人告诉了你多少...但我可以帮你。但首先，我们需要离开这里。",
      "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural"
    },
    {
      "frame": "https://lost-choices-art.tos-cn-beijing.volces.com/characters/lin_xiaowei/lin_xiaowei_face_01_20260222_041748_1.png",
      "text": "我知道这很难。但你必须做出选择。相信我，我带你安全离开。",
      "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural"
    },
    {
      "frame": "https://lost-choices-art.tos-cn-beijing.volces.com/scenes/ch1/sc_002/sc_002_env_01_20260222_091751_1.png",
      "text": "你准备好做出选择了吗？",
      "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural"
    }
  ]
}
